&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Gwyneth Paltrow began goop in the fall of 2008 as a weekly newsletter. It has expanded into a beauty, fashion, and food business&amp;nbsp;that’s&amp;nbsp;also known for its products, curation, podcast, TV shows, live events, and retail stores.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
